Qatar in Exclusive Talks for U.K.’s Silverstone Track, Independent Says

-- B y   P a t r i c i a   K u o
-- 
2011-08-28T10:25:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-28/qatar-in-exclusive-talks-for-u-k-race-track-independent-says.html
The Qatar Investment Authority is in
exclusive talks to buy Silverstone race track, home to British
Grand Prix, the Independent newspaper reported.  The British Racing Drivers’ Club is in negotiations to
lease the 850-acre site for 150 years in a deal worth as much as
250 million pounds ($409 million), the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Patricia Kuo in London at 
 pkuo2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
